1
00:00:06,430 --> 00:00:09,190
The same power, the same voice...

2
00:00:09,190 --> 00:00:11,670
I see. It's uncanny.

3
00:00:11,670 --> 00:00:14,660
That power interests me!

4
00:00:14,910 --> 00:00:16,760
Your very presence disgusts me!

5
00:00:16,760 --> 00:00:18,080
It is time I ended this.

6
00:01:56,550 --> 00:02:00,420
Professor Happy's Fairy Tail Lectures!

7
00:02:00,420 --> 00:02:04,770
This time, I'll be teaching you about 
Carla and myself's homeland, Edolas!

8
00:02:04,770 --> 00:02:08,220
The world we live in is called "Earthland"...

9
00:02:08,220 --> 00:02:10,230
Edolas is a different world.

10
00:02:10,230 --> 00:02:14,610
In Edolas, magic power is a limited 
resource that will one day be used up.

11
00:02:14,610 --> 00:02:16,460
Because of that, King Faust

12
00:02:16,460 --> 00:02:21,960
used the hyperspace magic Anima to 
absorb magic power from Earthland!

13
00:02:21,960 --> 00:02:25,270
The guild and people from Magnolia 
were turned into a lacrima,

14
00:02:25,270 --> 00:02:29,130
and we're all fighting 
to return them to normal.

15
00:02:29,130 --> 00:02:33,690
By the way, there's a separate set 
of Natsu and the others in Edolas.

16
00:02:33,690 --> 00:02:35,720
But the Erza in Edolas is our enemy!

17
00:02:35,720 --> 00:02:36,500
Scary, huh?

18
00:02:36,500 --> 00:02:38,020
Can't rest easy, huh?

19
00:02:38,020 --> 00:02:41,520
And there you have it. Let's 
get back to the story.

20
00:02:41,860 --> 00:02:43,590
Stand, bow...

21
00:02:43,590 --> 00:02:44,720
Aye, sir!

22
00:03:03,160 --> 00:03:05,290
Oh, it's her!

23
00:03:05,560 --> 00:03:07,580
Isn't that one of the Fallen?

24
00:03:07,580 --> 00:03:09,210
There's even a human!

25
00:03:09,210 --> 00:03:11,000
Whoa, I've never seen one before!

26
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:12,810
It's a human, a human!

27
00:03:13,120 --> 00:03:15,260
What is she doing here?

28
00:03:15,260 --> 00:03:16,910
What's going on?

29
00:03:16,910 --> 00:03:18,430
The Fallen one...

30
00:03:18,430 --> 00:03:21,260
brought a human...

31
00:03:23,680 --> 00:03:25,820
Please let me see the Queen!

32
00:03:26,270 --> 00:03:29,240
Extalia is in grave danger.

33
00:03:31,740 --> 00:03:34,160
The Doomsday Dragon Chain Cannon.

34
00:03:44,100 --> 00:03:45,680
Move it, move it!

35
00:03:45,680 --> 00:03:47,380
Let me through!

36
00:03:46,120 --> 00:03:47,380
N-Nady-sama!

37
00:03:47,380 --> 00:03:48,950
Good timing!

38
00:03:49,600 --> 00:03:51,220
This isn't good at all!

39
00:03:51,220 --> 00:03:54,980
The Fallen and Humans are 
forbidden from entering Extalia!

40
00:03:54,980 --> 00:03:57,320
This isn't the time for that.

41
00:03:57,320 --> 00:04:00,900
If you people value your lives, then listen.

42
00:04:00,900 --> 00:04:04,870
Where did Nichiya-san and the rest of 
the guards go that were chasing you?

43
00:04:04,870 --> 00:04:07,430
They've been turned into a 
lacrima by the Royal Army.

44
00:04:23,320 --> 00:04:27,770
Extalia's Royal Guard done in by some humans?

45
00:04:27,770 --> 00:04:30,050
You expect us to believe 
something as silly as that?

46
00:04:30,050 --> 00:04:33,620
It's the truth! The Royal Army 
will be attacking here shortly!

47
00:04:33,620 --> 00:04:35,570
So what?

48
00:04:35,570 --> 00:04:38,440
Our Queen will blow them 
all away with her magic!

49
00:04:38,440 --> 00:04:39,760
That's right!

50
00:04:41,170 --> 00:04:44,760
Everyone, if you don't escape, 
you'll all be in big trouble!

51
00:04:44,760 --> 00:04:46,590
Shut up, human!

52
00:04:47,670 --> 00:04:48,960
Wendy!

53
00:04:48,960 --> 00:04:51,480
You don't even know how 
powerful our Queen is!

54
00:04:51,480 --> 00:04:53,260
We're Exceeds!

55
00:04:53,260 --> 00:04:55,360
We're not like you humans!

56
00:04:56,390 --> 00:04:57,770
Stop it!

57
00:05:06,950 --> 00:05:09,130
Get out, Human! Get out, Fallen!

58
00:05:09,130 --> 00:05:12,490
This is the blessed land 
of our Queen, Extalia!

59
00:05:12,490 --> 00:05:14,010
We aren't going to lose to some humans!

60
00:05:14,010 --> 00:05:15,830
Not as long as our Queen is here!

61
00:05:20,680 --> 00:05:21,670
If...

62
00:05:21,670 --> 00:05:24,970
If you hate humans that much, 
do with me what you must!

63
00:05:24,970 --> 00:05:27,000
But Carla is different!

64
00:05:27,000 --> 00:05:29,180
She's one of you!

65
00:05:29,180 --> 00:05:32,660
Listen to what she says, please!

66
00:05:34,070 --> 00:05:35,680
Wendy...

67
00:05:35,680 --> 00:05:44,020
Get out! Get out! Get out! Get out...

68
00:05:53,830 --> 00:05:56,850
Why? Why?

69
00:06:07,340 --> 00:06:08,760
Gajeel!

70
00:06:14,280 --> 00:06:18,170
Unarmed, you can stop my iron-hard sword?

71
00:06:18,170 --> 00:06:21,780
Earthland magic is full of surprises.

72
00:06:21,780 --> 00:06:25,590
Sorry to break it to you, but an Iron 
Dragon's iron isn't normal iron.

73
00:06:25,590 --> 00:06:28,860
Anyway, aren't you one of the cats?

74
00:06:28,860 --> 00:06:31,490
Why're you working for the Royal Army?

75
00:06:32,920 --> 00:06:34,990
U-Um...

76
00:06:35,240 --> 00:06:38,960
You're an Exceed like me, right?

77
00:06:40,380 --> 00:06:43,210
Would... you like a fish?

78
00:06:44,870 --> 00:06:46,550
That's in the past.

79
00:06:48,400 --> 00:06:50,220
I have forsaken my homeland!

80
00:06:50,220 --> 00:06:52,570
That fake country!

81
00:06:59,310 --> 00:07:01,690
Fake country...?

82
00:07:03,250 --> 00:07:05,600
An outcast, huh?

83
00:07:05,600 --> 00:07:08,690
I like it. Same as me.

84
00:07:17,350 --> 00:07:18,580
I like your style!

85
00:07:26,720 --> 00:07:29,890
I'm gonna make this guy my cat!

86
00:07:30,640 --> 00:07:32,720
My Buster Maam!

87
00:07:36,890 --> 00:07:40,020
But first I gotta show you 
which one of us is stronger!

88
00:07:40,570 --> 00:07:44,370
Uh, I think his switch just flipped on.

89
00:07:45,770 --> 00:07:50,600
I won't be outdone by Salamander 
or that little girl!

90
00:07:50,600 --> 00:07:51,780
He's...

91
00:07:51,780 --> 00:07:54,130
Roar of the Iron Dragon!

92
00:08:06,120 --> 00:08:09,050
Gajeel's looking scary!

93
00:08:13,750 --> 00:08:15,800
That's how it's gotta be.

94
00:08:18,310 --> 00:08:19,390
You're strong.

95
00:08:34,460 --> 00:08:38,370
Gajeel... Are you forgetting why 
we're here in the first place?

96
00:08:46,950 --> 00:08:49,620
I'm an Ice Maker Magic wizard.

97
00:08:49,620 --> 00:08:51,500
I can make as many keys as I need.

98
00:08:53,680 --> 00:08:55,240
Gray!

99
00:08:55,240 --> 00:08:55,970
Natsu!

100
00:08:57,180 --> 00:08:59,160
Finally caught up to the bastard!

101
00:08:59,160 --> 00:09:01,060
I told you to leave him to me, remember?

102
00:09:01,060 --> 00:09:03,100
Where's the key?

103
00:09:03,100 --> 00:09:04,210
Hand it over, you!

104
00:09:04,210 --> 00:09:05,610
You chinny bastard!

105
00:09:05,610 --> 00:09:09,020
Um... Can't you see what I have in my hand?

106
00:09:09,270 --> 00:09:11,200
Anyway, we're fine.

107
00:09:11,200 --> 00:09:13,460
The situation has changed a bit.

108
00:09:13,460 --> 00:09:14,820
Where's Lucy?

109
00:09:16,270 --> 00:09:17,610
Oh, right...

110
00:09:17,610 --> 00:09:18,840
She's stuck.

111
00:09:18,840 --> 00:09:20,160
Stuck? What?

112
00:09:20,160 --> 00:09:21,990
Just a little more!

113
00:09:21,990 --> 00:09:24,750
Your boobs are huge!

114
00:09:25,310 --> 00:09:28,210
Anyway, Natsu... We can use this key!

115
00:09:28,210 --> 00:09:30,920
We can use it to save all of our friends!

116
00:09:30,920 --> 00:09:31,940
What?

117
00:09:31,940 --> 00:09:34,130
Their plan was to use the Dragon Chain cannon

118
00:09:34,130 --> 00:09:37,940
to pull the lacrima island 
and ram it into Extalia.

119
00:09:39,270 --> 00:09:40,370
But!

120
00:09:43,120 --> 00:09:45,890
If we crash the Dragon Chain Cannon, 
infused with Dragon Slayer magic,

121
00:09:45,890 --> 00:09:48,230
directly into the lacrima...

122
00:09:49,650 --> 00:09:51,810
...we can return everyone to normal!

123
00:09:51,810 --> 00:09:55,320
Oh! I don't get it, but I see!

124
00:09:55,590 --> 00:09:57,390
The Dragon Chain Cannon seems to be up ahead.

125
00:09:57,390 --> 00:09:59,890
Right, let's go.

126
00:09:59,890 --> 00:10:01,570
We have a problem though.

127
00:10:03,120 --> 00:10:05,750
There's no way to enter the room.

128
00:10:05,750 --> 00:10:08,160
Then we just bust our way in, right?

129
00:10:08,160 --> 00:10:10,330
I can use magic now, remember?

130
00:10:11,090 --> 00:10:12,790
Not gonna work.

131
00:10:12,790 --> 00:10:20,340
There's some kind of "Wizard Canceler" 
device that makes it so magic won't work.

132
00:10:20,340 --> 00:10:22,660
Won't know until we try, right?

133
00:10:22,660 --> 00:10:24,470
We need a plan, first!

134
00:10:32,760 --> 00:10:34,860
So there you are...

135
00:10:34,860 --> 00:10:36,420
Erza!

136
00:10:36,420 --> 00:10:40,380
Wait... That's the Edolas's...

137
00:10:42,070 --> 00:10:43,500
Damn it...

138
00:10:44,830 --> 00:10:49,540
Our Erza... lost?

139
00:11:01,510 --> 00:11:04,190
Are you well, Captain Knightwalker?

140
00:11:04,190 --> 00:11:05,610
Well? Look at her!

141
00:11:05,610 --> 00:11:08,360
W-Where did you get those wounds?

142
00:11:08,360 --> 00:11:10,020
Just a few scratches.

143
00:11:10,020 --> 00:11:11,990
And those two...?

144
00:11:11,990 --> 00:11:13,860
The key to the Dragon Chain Cannon.

145
00:11:13,860 --> 00:11:15,900
K-Key?

146
00:11:15,900 --> 00:11:17,620
Is His Highness inside?

147
00:11:17,620 --> 00:11:20,150
Yes! This way.

148
00:11:25,740 --> 00:11:28,170
All the preparations are complete.

149
00:11:28,900 --> 00:11:32,110
An eternity of magic, right before my eyes...

150
00:11:46,510 --> 00:11:49,010
Damn, he's slow.

151
00:11:49,010 --> 00:11:51,410
Hey, you call out to her!

152
00:11:51,410 --> 00:11:53,070
R-Right...

153
00:11:54,110 --> 00:11:56,890
H-Hey, what are you doing there?

154
00:11:56,890 --> 00:11:58,630
Everyone's waiting.

155
00:11:58,630 --> 00:12:00,150
My informant.

156
00:12:00,150 --> 00:12:01,940
W-What?

157
00:12:01,940 --> 00:12:04,020
Plotting something again?

158
00:12:04,020 --> 00:12:09,310
I need the latest information... if I'm 
going to convince everyone, anyway.

159
00:12:09,310 --> 00:12:10,830
Convince us?

160
00:12:10,830 --> 00:12:12,730
I don't like the sound of that.

161
00:12:13,130 --> 00:12:15,100
How is everyone doing?

162
00:12:15,100 --> 00:12:18,980
They heard you had something to 
say, Lucy-san, so they're uneasy.

163
00:12:18,980 --> 00:12:20,250
No kidding.

164
00:12:20,250 --> 00:12:24,760
After meeting those guys from the other 
world, Lucy's been more uptight than ever!

165
00:12:24,760 --> 00:12:27,440
Yeah... That'd scare anyone, for sure...

166
00:12:27,440 --> 00:12:29,970
You bunch of goddamn scaredy-cats!

167
00:12:30,210 --> 00:12:31,800
We're sorry!

168
00:12:31,800 --> 00:12:33,070
Don't harmonize!

169
00:12:51,300 --> 00:12:55,110
Erza, is it true you bring the key with you?

170
00:12:55,110 --> 00:12:57,560
It was destroyed, but do not worry.

171
00:12:57,560 --> 00:12:58,500
What?

172
00:13:00,760 --> 00:13:02,740
He can make a key.

173
00:13:02,740 --> 00:13:03,890
Damn you...

174
00:13:03,890 --> 00:13:05,040
And he is...?

175
00:13:05,040 --> 00:13:06,970
An Earthland wizard.

176
00:13:06,970 --> 00:13:09,200
A friend of the Dragon Slayer.

177
00:13:10,960 --> 00:13:12,450
Are you saying...

178
00:13:12,450 --> 00:13:15,220
They have something to do with the 
disappearance of the lacrima in the public square?

179
00:13:15,220 --> 00:13:16,600
Exactly.

180
00:13:17,960 --> 00:13:19,600
Fine then.

181
00:13:19,600 --> 00:13:21,690
Activate the Dragon Chain Cannon immediately.

182
00:13:23,610 --> 00:13:25,370
Stand, Ice Wizard.

183
00:13:25,370 --> 00:13:27,330
And don't try anything funny.

184
00:13:31,830 --> 00:13:34,330
Activate the Dragon Chain Cannon.

185
00:13:40,610 --> 00:13:42,840
This is the Dragon Chain Cannon?

186
00:13:43,540 --> 00:13:46,970
It's a whole lot different than I'd imagined.

187
00:13:47,290 --> 00:13:50,370
On a much bigger scale, for sure...

188
00:13:52,260 --> 00:13:53,390
Hurry and do it!

189
00:13:55,280 --> 00:13:57,100
I don't have any choice...

190
00:14:03,210 --> 00:14:05,040
W-Whoa...

191
00:14:05,040 --> 00:14:06,490
Is that Earthland magic?

192
00:14:06,490 --> 00:14:08,550
But, why is he naked?

193
00:14:08,550 --> 00:14:11,570
I should charge admission for this!

194
00:14:21,260 --> 00:14:23,040
I only have one chance.

195
00:14:31,460 --> 00:14:35,050
I'll smash the Dragon Chain Cannon 
straight into the lacrima!

196
00:14:36,290 --> 00:14:42,080
That way we can save all our friends, 
and everyone from Magnolia!

197
00:14:48,860 --> 00:14:51,860
Yes, that's wonderful!

198
00:15:27,890 --> 00:15:29,990
The castle is transforming?!

199
00:15:29,990 --> 00:15:31,730
What in the world is going on?

200
00:15:31,730 --> 00:15:33,110
It's started!

201
00:15:33,360 --> 00:15:35,950
The Dragon Chain Cannon has been activated!

202
00:15:35,950 --> 00:15:38,540
It's almost like the Gildarts Shift!

203
00:15:38,540 --> 00:15:41,830
What insane idiot came up with this?

204
00:15:41,830 --> 00:15:43,470
The King!

205
00:15:44,590 --> 00:15:47,110
How do I change the aim?

206
00:15:51,170 --> 00:15:52,360
Where?!

207
00:16:06,110 --> 00:16:08,600
That's the Dragon Chain Cannon?

208
00:16:09,280 --> 00:16:12,530
Things are proceeding 
faster than I anticipated.

209
00:16:13,410 --> 00:16:16,690
This is bad! I must hurry!

210
00:16:16,950 --> 00:16:18,950
Prepare to fire!

211
00:16:18,950 --> 00:16:20,120
Crap!

212
00:16:24,170 --> 00:16:25,330
This is it.

213
00:16:25,330 --> 00:16:26,330
Natsu!

214
00:16:29,860 --> 00:16:31,300
Right on!

215
00:16:31,650 --> 00:16:32,550
What?

216
00:16:32,550 --> 00:16:36,470
Wing Slash of the Fire Dragon!

217
00:16:39,240 --> 00:16:43,270
What is the meaning of this?

218
00:16:47,060 --> 00:16:49,070
Stop the launch!

219
00:16:49,070 --> 00:16:51,110
Erza! You fiend!

220
00:16:57,530 --> 00:17:00,100
What treachery is this, Erza?!

221
00:17:06,020 --> 00:17:08,130
I am Erza Scarlet!

222
00:17:08,130 --> 00:17:09,630
Earthland's Erza!

223
00:17:12,470 --> 00:17:16,930
Sorry about that. Your quick 
thinking helped us out.

224
00:17:18,480 --> 00:17:21,310
This was plan D! D for Dupe the Dolts!

225
00:17:24,060 --> 00:17:27,260
Aim the Dragon Chain Cannon at the lacrima!

226
00:17:27,260 --> 00:17:29,020
Do not listen to her!

227
00:17:29,020 --> 00:17:30,310
Fire it immediately!

228
00:17:31,900 --> 00:17:32,990
What'll we do?

229
00:17:32,990 --> 00:17:36,210
Taking a hostage? That's low!

230
00:17:36,210 --> 00:17:38,480
Oh, yeah?

231
00:17:38,480 --> 00:17:42,200
We'll do whatever it takes 
to save our friends!

232
00:17:42,710 --> 00:17:44,040
Hurry and do it, or else...

233
00:17:45,710 --> 00:17:47,520
Do it! Our Highness is in danger!

234
00:17:47,520 --> 00:17:49,020
Do not mind me!

235
00:17:49,020 --> 00:17:51,840
Fire it, in order to destroy the Exceed!

236
00:17:51,840 --> 00:17:53,840
Readjust the aim!

237
00:17:53,840 --> 00:17:56,150
Change it to hit the giant lacrima!

238
00:18:03,580 --> 00:18:05,720
You fools!

239
00:18:05,720 --> 00:18:08,770
You're going to throw away 
an eternity of magic power?

240
00:18:11,110 --> 00:18:14,230
Scarlet!

241
00:18:16,900 --> 00:18:19,070
Knightwalker!

242
00:18:19,070 --> 00:18:21,330
His Highness has been freed!

243
00:18:21,330 --> 00:18:24,320
Now, revert the aim back!

244
00:18:30,960 --> 00:18:32,460
Crap!

245
00:18:33,460 --> 00:18:36,440
Knightwalker, you're still...

246
00:18:36,440 --> 00:18:39,990
This isn't over yet, Scarlet!

247
00:18:39,990 --> 00:18:42,990
Fire!!

248
00:19:47,270 --> 00:19:48,530
What the...

249
00:19:51,580 --> 00:19:54,040
The Dragon Chain Cannon has connected...

250
00:19:54,630 --> 00:19:56,040
We didn't make it!

251
00:19:57,120 --> 00:20:00,840
What the... Something huge has stuck on!

252
00:20:04,640 --> 00:20:06,970
O-Oh, no!

253
00:20:09,850 --> 00:20:11,470
Grappling complete!

254
00:20:11,470 --> 00:20:14,230
Ram it into Extalia!

255
00:20:14,230 --> 00:20:17,610
Don't!!!

256
00:20:23,270 --> 00:20:24,520
Everyone!

257
00:20:26,910 --> 00:20:28,850
Everyone, get on!

258
00:20:28,850 --> 00:20:29,670
Lucy?

259
00:20:29,670 --> 00:20:30,680
Where are you?

260
00:20:30,680 --> 00:20:33,330
You turned into a giant monster?

261
00:20:33,330 --> 00:20:35,420
Stop your blabbing and get on board!

262
00:20:35,420 --> 00:20:36,920
A Legion!

263
00:20:36,920 --> 00:20:38,690
Why is it here?

264
00:20:38,690 --> 00:20:41,920
How can that girl ride a Legion?

265
00:20:41,920 --> 00:20:43,610
This Legion is mine!

266
00:20:43,610 --> 00:20:44,840
Coco...

267
00:20:45,470 --> 00:20:47,510
Can we stop it?

268
00:20:47,510 --> 00:20:49,680
I don't know, but we have to go!

269
00:20:49,680 --> 00:20:50,390
Yeah.

270
00:20:56,270 --> 00:20:58,790
D-Don't run!

271
00:21:08,120 --> 00:21:10,610
Scarlet...

272
00:21:14,370 --> 00:21:15,700
After her!

273
00:21:15,700 --> 00:21:18,930
Legion Squad of the Second 
Magic Regiment, move out!

274
00:21:20,620 --> 00:21:22,480
I shall go as well.

275
00:21:23,160 --> 00:21:25,560
Get Droma Anim ready!

276
00:21:26,960 --> 00:21:29,400
T-That's a forbidden craft...

277
00:21:29,400 --> 00:21:34,710
It's strictly forbidden under the 
Charter of the Kingdom, Article 23!

278
00:21:34,710 --> 00:21:37,080
Get it ready!

279
00:21:50,450 --> 00:21:52,110
What the...

280
00:21:52,110 --> 00:21:53,720
Are we moving?

281
00:21:53,720 --> 00:21:55,950
This is our army's plan.

282
00:21:56,540 --> 00:22:01,830
We will ram this lacrima into Extalia, 
and they will annihilate each other.

283
00:22:04,010 --> 00:22:05,860
That's nuts.

284
00:22:05,860 --> 00:22:07,570
This is messed up.

285
00:22:07,570 --> 00:22:08,970
How?

286
00:22:10,310 --> 00:22:14,120
How can you do something so horrible?

287
00:22:17,170 --> 00:22:21,480
Hurry!!!

288
00:23:55,990 --> 00:23:57,760
I'm gonna stop it, for sure!

289
00:23:57,760 --> 00:24:01,770
I ain't gonna let a single person in Fairy 
Tail or a single Exceed be sacrificed!

290
00:24:01,770 --> 00:24:02,820
Aye, sir!

291
00:24:02,820 --> 00:24:04,500
Let's go!

292
00:24:04,500 --> 00:24:08,630
By the way, I found an extremely 
rare fish the other day.

293
00:24:08,630 --> 00:24:10,260
Let's go catch it next time!

294
00:24:10,260 --> 00:24:11,140
Huh? What?

295
00:24:11,140 --> 00:24:14,330
You know, that time we 
all went to the mountain?

296
00:24:14,330 --> 00:24:16,810
Next time: The Boy Back Then.

297
00:24:16,810 --> 00:24:19,640
So you're saying we have to go right now?

298
00:24:19,640 --> 00:24:21,140
The early worm catches the fish!

299
00:24:21,140 --> 00:24:22,230
No, no, no...

300
00:24:22,230 --> 00:24:24,190
This is <i>so</i> not the time.

